Author: InSkyLimitEra
Text: I’m experiencing things from the other side. I’m currently a sub-intern on a general psych inpatient unit that includes EDO patients. Stomach was definitely grumbling during patient interviews this morning... luckily I think it was only really noticeable once or twice.

Author: Liza_8989
Text: I experienced something similar... I went to a psychiatric to get medication for panic attacks and my stupid ed brain made me ask if I could gain weigh with the medication and if the pills had calories... oh well
